{"tid":890164,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港咁樣 真係會令我街都唔想出","createTime":"2018-11-05T06:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T11:58:59.000Z","uid":203163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d429773fee966c470c0b6bac6ded529a8ee29a","tid":890164,"uid":203163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/05/140817_6a86fcb2582d3afcb4dc3faaa6892491.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F140817_6a86fcb2582d3afcb4dc3faaa6892491.png&h=d8e109c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ndllm 大陸閪<br />\n都唔知你地黎撚曬香港做乜撚野<br />\n到底香港有乜撚野吸引<br />\n要你地成批成批咁過黎<br />\n搞到條街烏煙瘴氣<br />\n仲要周圍因為人多而逼撚住曬<br />\n其實依家真係好撚憎去多大陸人嘅香港地方<br />\n行步路都難<br />\n我真係屌曬你地老母<br />\n死大陸閪"},{"pid":"08e210edf9d729618d2792f4cd369080e0738e69","tid":890164,"uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"而家先唔想出？咁你一定係住東涌喇<br />\n<br />\n沙田友上水友表示無出街好撚耐，搞光復果陣仲比人吊搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家係時候到西九圓方同東涌撚感受係中國人的榮耀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77d03d54cff338f2df690e36161a5f0e68f69de","tid":890164,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"屯門、元朗牛笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}